Generate playlists

Usage:
  radio playlist init NAME
  radio playlist generate NAME
  radio playlist --help

Commands:
  init
    Create a playlist configuration file. This step is required prior to using
    the generate command.

  generate
    Generate a playlist file based on the configuration file.

Options:
  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  NAME
    The name of the playlist without any extension

Examples:
  radio playlist init MyRockMusic
  radio playlist generate MyRockMusic
